

Aabshaar = Waterfall
Zarkhaizi-e-zameen = fertility of land/soil

khoobsurat to bahut lagta hai, behta aabshaar dekhne mein
Par jaan lo haath hai usika zarkhaizi-e-zameen churane mein

AC BUY ANALYSIS

Finally after Market research ordered "Carrier Hybridjet CAI18BR5C8F0"
What pulled me to buy this ?
1. Many buyers in flipkart and also reviews are good.
2. Good will from my colleages who are already using the product.
3. Less price comapred to Hitachi & Daikin.
4. customer care was active @ ODD time i.e. 7:00 in the morning (TOLL FREE TOO).
5. Have all the features like: 
	1. Have hidden display (which is present onlyin JTK series
		of daikin)
	2. Refrigerant Leakage Detector
	3. Auto on Timer
		It lets you select a particular time to switch on the AC automatically.
	4. PM2.5 filter + auto cleanser
	5. auto turn off, stabilizer free & cools even at 52-degree C
	6. Good warranty compred to others
	   1 Year on Complete Unit, 10 Years on Compressor and 2 Years on ODU Printed Circuit Board

cons:
Uses R410a refrigrant instead of R32 eco friendly & power consumption friendly as used in Daikin
